text: Tibaldi is an Italian surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Maria Felice Tibaldi (born 1707), Italian painter * Pellegrino Tibaldi (1527–1596), Italian mannerist architect, sculptor, and mural painter * Giovanni Battista Tibaldi (circa 1660 – 1736), Italian violinist and composer ==See also== * Tebaldi
title: Tibaldi
